        User = U1 + U2
        Influencer = none
        Photo = P1 + P2
        Ad = P1
        Day = D1

        follows = U2->U1
        posts = U1->P1 + U1->P2
        sees = U1->P1 + U2->P1 + U2->P2
        suggested = none

        date = P1->D1 + P2->D1
    }
} for 2 User, 2 Photo, 1 Day expect 1

valid:
run Pos2 {
    some disj WS1, WS2 : Workstation | some disj WK1, WK2 : Worker | some disj P1, P2 : Product {
        Workstation = WS1 + WS2
        begin = WS1
        end = WS2
        succ = none->none

        Worker = WK1 + WK2
        Human = none
        Robot = WK1 + WK2
        workers = WS1->WK1 + WS2->WK2

        Product = P1 + P2
        Component = P1 + P2
        Material = none
        Dangerous = none

        parts = P1->P2 + P2->P1            // neither component is its own part
        workstation = P1->WS1 + P2->WS2
    }
} for 2 Workstation, 2 Worker, 2 Product expect 1

parse:
run Pos1 {
  some disj P1,P2 : Person | some disj C1 : Course | some disj G1,G2 : Grade {
    Person = P1 + P2
    Professor = P2
    Student = P1
    Course = C1
    Project = none
    Grade = G1 + G2

    Person <: teaches = P2->C1
    Person <: enrolled = P1->C1
    Person <: projects = none
    Course <: projects = none
    Course <: grades = C1->P1->G1
    Grade <: next = G1->G2
  }
} for 2 Person, 1 Course, 0 Project, 2 Grade expect 1

run Pos2 {
  some disj P1,P2 : Person | some disj C1,C2 : Course | some disj Pr1 : Project | some disj G1,G2 : Grade {

    Professor = none
    Student = P1 + P2
    Course = C1 + C2
    Project = Pr1
    Grade = G1 + G2

    Person <: teaches = none
    Person <: enrolled = P1->C1 + P2->C2
    Person <: projects = P1->Pr1 + P2->Pr1
    Course <: projects = C1->Pr1 + C2->Pr1
    Course <: grades = C1->P1->G2 + C2->P2->G1
    Grade <: next = G1->G2

previous:

  some disj P1, P2, S1, S2 : Person | some disj C1, C2 : Course | some disj PR1, PR2 : Project | some disj G0, G1, G2 : Grade {
    Person = P1 + P2 + S1 + S2
    Professor = P1 + P2
    Student = S1 + S2
    Course = C1 + C2
    Project = PR1 + PR2
    Grade = G0 + G1 + G2

    Person <: teaches = P1->C1 + P2->C2
    Person <: enrolled = S1->C1 + S2->C2
    Person <: projects = S1->PR1 + S2->PR2

    Course <: projects = C1->PR1 + C2->PR2
    Course <: grades = C1->S1->G1 + C2->S2->G2 + C2->S1->G0
